OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be largely cloudy
OL,6,Fthrough the day with some showery
OL,7,Foutbreaks of rain which may turn heavy
OL,8,Fat times.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FIt will remain cloudy through
OL,11,Fthe evening and overnight with some
OL,12,Fshowery outbreaks of rain, heavy at
OL,13,Ffirst, gradually easing overnight.
OL,14,
OL,15,CSunday:FDull and cloudy with some
OL,16,Flight rain in the morning. Some
OL,17,Fbrighter spells may develop later.
OL,18,FChance of a heavy shower in the
OL,19,Fsouthwest. Feeling cool in the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
